name: Bougainvillea spectabilis, No. 2
description:
This black and white silver gelatin print is part of a series I photographed and developed when I spent some time in Hawaii. 

The tropical environment was filled with colorfully eye-popping indigenous and introduced flora. I focused on the forms and textures of the beautifully enchanting plants I encountered.
